{"type": "article", "id": 3635, "title": "HAY 收纳挂饰", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-18T08:05:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232701M9HtG5PxUuyOv0wp.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自巴黎的设计师 Inga Sempé 今年为丹麦家居品牌 Hay 设计了一款名为「Pinoram」的收纳挂饰，可以为用户收纳一些随手可能会用到的小物件。Pinoram 的背部时一个软木材质的长方体，外立面被砖纹穿孔金属结构包裹，形成了一个个的小型网格。Pinoram 的方便之处在于其模块化的设计，使得用户可以按照自己的需要添加额外的存储组建与配件，因为背部是软木塞的缘故，包括磁铁、别针等都可以用来固定备忘录、便签条等。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052326584bWSAKJ65PVTGlEj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232658z4Vl1E9mZdbItUk8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232659hw0DvOErL4S761Fk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232659RBtXG5UdCT1VHkQ3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232700Q8xCLAbor9qal7gR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232700gfPyvDSO9TRIHZ5h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}